OL,3,CTrust to pause hospital consultation
OL,4,Cafter Health Minister intervenes
OL,6,FThe Western Trust has decided to pause
OL,7,Fits consultation into the permanent
OL,8,Fremoval of emergency general surgery
OL,9,Ffrom the South West Acute Hospital.
OL,11,FIt comes after the Health Minister
OL,12,Fstepped in and urged it to be
OL,13,Fsuspended, saying he was
OL,14,F"disappointed" in the process.
OL,16,FEmergency general surgery was first
OL,17,Fsuspended from the South West Acute
OL,18,FHospital back in December 2022, with
OL,19,Fpatients instead having to travel to
OL,20,FAltnagelvin Area Hospital outside
OL,21,FLondonderry.
