OL,6,FAt the time, the Western. Trust
OL,7,Finsisted the move was necessary to
OL,8,Fprotect patient safety after it
OL,9,Fstruggled to recruit enough surgeons
OL,10,Fto the Fermanagh area.
OL,12,FTwo weeks ago, a consultation was
OL,13,Fopened over proposals to permanently
OL,14,Fwithdraw emergency general surgery
OL,15,Ffrom the hospital.
