OL,3,CTrust to pause hospital consultation
OL,4,Cafter Health Minister intervenes
OL,6,FHowever, the Health Minister Mike
OL,7,FNesbitt intervened, writing to Trust
OL,8,Fofficials saying he was "deeply
OL,9,Fdisappointed that the process" had
OL,10,F"been besieged by so many obvious
OL,11,Fshortcomings and mistakes".
OL,13,FThe letter was first revealed by the
OL,14,FImpartial Reporter newspaper.
OL,16,FIn a fresh statement to UTV, the
OL,17,FDepartment of Health said the Minister
OL,18,Fhad asked the trust to "pause a
OL,19,Fconsultation" and "to act quickly to
OL,20,Frestore confidence"
