OL,3,CTrust to pause hospital consultation
OL,4,Cafter Health Minister intervenes
OL,6,FHelen Hamill, a campaigner for Save
OL,7,Four Acute Services, said: "It has
OL,8,Fcertainly created a tidal wave of
OL,9,Freactions on our social media feeds
OL,10,Fand in the community in general.
OL,12,F"And we do hope that the Western Trust
OL,13,Facts on the statement. And again, we
OL,14,Fhope that the minister uses his powers
OL,15,Fto to to see that they do so."
OL,17,FShortly after UTV spoke to Ms Hamill,
OL,18,Fthe Trust revealed it would be pausing
OL,19,Fits consultation following a meeting
OL,20,Fof the Trust Board, saying it would
OL,21,Freconsider its consultation approach.
