OL,3,CTrust to pause hospital consultation
OL,4,Cafter Health Minister intervenes
OL,6,F"We fully respect the Minister's
OL,7,Frequest this week to take cognisance
OL,8,Fof the feedback to date around the
OL,9,Fcontent, scheduling and timescales of
OL,10,Fthe consultation process," a statement
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"The Trust supported by the DoH
OL,14,Fremains fully committed to the long
OL,15,Fterm development and vision for SWAH.
OL,16,Fthe Trust would highlight that the
OL,17,FSouth West Acute Hospital continues to
OL,18,Fbe a successful acute hospital,
OL,19,Fproviding high quality care with a
OL,20,FConsultant-led Emergency Department.
