OL,3,CTrust to pause hospital consultation
OL,4,Cafter Health Minister intervenes
OL,6,F"It is important for the public to
OL,7,Fnote that the temporary emergency
OL,8,Ftransfer of general surgery to
OL,9,FAltnagelvin Hospital continues to be
OL,10,Fin place.
OL,12,F"In conclusion the Board does wish to
OL,13,Fapologise for the uncertainly that has
OL,14,Fbeen created for the public as a
OL,15,Fresult of these events and clearly our
OL,16,Fcommitment is to address these issues
OL,17,Fand through a revised process of
OL,18,Fconsultation and engagement."
